// Template for local signing config.
//
// Copy this file to `Local.xcconfig` (which is gitignored) and fill in your
// own values. project.yml reads signing from Local.xcconfig, so `xcodegen
// generate` will never overwrite your personal team / bundle id again.
//
//   cp Local.xcconfig.example Local.xcconfig
//   # then edit the two values below
//
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM: your Apple Developer Team ID (Xcode → Settings → Accounts →
//   your team → "Team ID"). Leave empty to sign manually / build for simulator.
// PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER: the app's bundle id (must be unique to your team).

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =
PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER = net.1x0.isNestle
